  "id": "RAW_8a948c6a",
  "title": "AGI，不会通知你",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247514016&idx=1&sn=b92998ef17793fcb869231c5cf57d8ae",
  "date": "2026-03-07 05:43:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f9d07e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdjGOVOCkFXeLSKhQNAriaG8U2BUgDXLiaEMnNP3wmDVeoRMFqcQGy90plEGEVd8rND9bxb5B8WHbC03P1AVFa7lYQdIWHhrOH3t0%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每次技术革命，都用上次的速度，欺骗这次的人</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">回望历史，我们发现每次技术革命都不是以宣布的方式到来</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是农业革命、工业革命，还是互联网革命，都是这样，我们总是在事情发生之后，才回过头来指出：哦，那是「xx革命」的起点</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AGI 也不会有例外，它到来的时候并不会通知你，而当你发现的时候，它已经过了，然后很多事情在各个角度并行发生着变化</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有一个更细思极恐的：核武器出现后，人们用了 20 年去摸清如何确保安全，但这一次，历史可能不会给到我们 20 年</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果是对于个人来说，这个窗口期可能会更短</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 18.2px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(185, 86, 0);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">门槛已经在身后了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1793年，英国派马戛尔尼勋爵出使大清，要求开放通商口岸。乾隆给英王乔治三世写了一封回信，语气平和，措辞妥帖：「天朝物产丰盈，无所不有，原不藉外夷货物以通有无」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">写这封信的时候，英国纺织厂里的蒸汽机已经轰鸣了将近三十年。乾隆不知道这件事，也不觉得需要知道。他用的是一套运转了几千年的框架，在那个框架里，大清是世界的中心，外夷是来朝贡的</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">五十年后，鸦片战争爆发</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AGI 不会有一个到来的时刻，只有一个回头看的时刻</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有一个研究机构叫 Meter，专门追踪一件事：给 AI 一个完整任务，全程不介入，看它能独立撑多久</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2024年初，前沿模型能可靠完成的任务在几分钟量级，相当于查一个问题、写一段代码。到2025年，这个数字到了五到十小时，相当于一个工程师独立完成一个完整功能模块的时间，这些数字每七个月翻一番，曲线没有趋平的迹象</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这段时间，由于项目需要，在一些前沿的实验室有过不少交流，渐渐地就觉得门槛可能离我们不远了，甚至说：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: #c66e4a;font-weight: bold;\">这个门槛已经开始变得模糊</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">我并不知道会有哪一天，会有怎样的方式，社会共识会告诉我们：AGI 已到达</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 18.2px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(185, 86, 0);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次的速度不在同一量级</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">公元前356年，商鞅在秦国开始变法。他重新丈量土地、废除贵族世袭、推行军功授爵。二十年后，商鞅被车裂而死。又过了一百年，秦始皇才统一六国</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">商鞅变法的果实，种树的人等不到</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1765年，瓦特改良了蒸汽机。纺织厂开始用机器代替手工，煤矿开始用机器抽水。英国第一部限制童工工时的工厂法，到1833年才通过</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从蒸汽机到工厂法，用了将近七十年</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1870年代，第二次工业革命在德国和美国同时爆发，普法战争打完，俾斯麦拿到赔款和煤矿，转身就开始建钢厂</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">德国从一个农业国变成欧洲最大的工业国，用了不到三十年</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1994年，中国接入互联网，第一封电子邮件从北京发出。十年后，淘宝上线。又十年，微信月活十亿</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从第一封电子邮件到改变所有人的日常生活，用了二十年</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2022年11月，ChatGPT 发布，两个月后两亿用户。然后到了2025年，连这个速度都开始显得慢了。Manus 上线不到一年，被以数十亿美金收购。OpenClaw，AGI Bar 社区里大家叫它小龙虾，从第一次被人知道，到 GitHub Star 数超过 Linux，只用了一个月。Linux 是全世界程序员用了三十年积累起来的信仰</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">每次技术革命，都在用上次的速度，欺骗这次的人</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一次，人类建立应对机制的速度都比技术慢，但最终能追上</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但对于这一次...我不知道</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 18.2px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(185, 86, 0);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全问题的答案在政治里</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1952年12月，伦敦被一层浓厚的烟雾笼罩了五天，能见度低到公交车司机需要乘客在前面打手电筒引路。五天之内，四千多人死去，后续数月又有八千人陆续离世</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术层面，解决方案早就存在。丘吉尔的内阁看完报告，把它搁置了。工业游说团体说改造成本太高，财政部说现在不是时候，卫生部说死亡数字属于正常的冬季水平。又死了四年人，《清洁空气法》才在1956年通过</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这段历史，在我们课本中被压缩到了四个字：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">伦敦大雾</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而放在当时，这是一个国家、一个时代的痛</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「多危险算太危险」，从来都不是工程师能回答的问题</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">蒸汽机不会告诉你排放多少二氧化硫算超标。这个数字需要医生去统计死亡人数，需要记者去报道，需要公众去抗议，需要议员去投票，每一个环节都是人和人之间的博弈</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也许，我们仍然还需要经历无数教训，才能找到安全的答案</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 18.2px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(185, 86, 0);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次没有二十年</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1962年10月，苏联在古巴部署核导弹的消息传到华盛顿</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来十三天，是人类历史上离核战争最近的时刻。肯尼迪和赫鲁晓夫之间的电报往来，今天读起来仍然让人背脊发凉，两个人都清楚，一旦两边产生一丁点的误判，我们可能会走向终点</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还好，现在以上帝视角来看，一切平稳度过</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在此之前，两国已经用将近二十年，经历了柏林封锁、朝鲜战争、一次次擦边球，在真实的高压对抗中摸索出彼此的边界。赫鲁晓夫知道能退到哪里，肯尼迪知道不能逼到哪里</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个「知道」，是用二十年的试探换来的</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">那二十年里，兰德公司建立了整套核威慑理论，热线电话被架设起来，第一轮军控谈判开始了。一套框架，从无到有</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">人类用了二十年，才在核武器出现后摸清楚彼此的边界，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而面对 AGI 的风险，我们这次没有二十年</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">等危机真的出现，可能没有十三天来回发电报，1950年代的兰德公司知道自己在做什么。对应的工作，我们现在还不知道是什么</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 18.2px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(185, 86, 0);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">新工具最先属于旧信任</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1455年，古腾堡印出了第一批《圣经》。在这之前，欧洲的书籍由修道院僧侣手工抄写，一本《圣经》需要几个月。印刷机出现之后，第一批大规模使用它的，是教会。他们印赎罪券、印教皇诏书、印弥撒手册，掌握最广泛传播渠道的机构，最快地把新工具用到了极致</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1517年，马丁·路德把《九十五条论纲》钉到教堂门上。这份文件能在两周内传遍整个德意志，靠的正是教会花了几十年建立起来的那套印刷和传播网络。路德用教会建立的基础设施，动摇了教会本身</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最快拿到新工具的人，永远是在旧工具上建立了最深信任的人</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">杠杆放大的是已有的优势</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">信任是慢变量，不会因为某个工具出现就突然产生。框架还没建好，规范还没到位，这段时间里，信任是少数几件可以提前做的事</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个窗口现在还开着</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border: none;height: 1px;color: inherit;margin: 2em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这五条判断，我不能保证是对的</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.6;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.85;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果方向大体没错，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: 600;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(185, 86, 0);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">留给调整的时间，可能比大多数人认为的要短</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过历史纵向对比，指出 AGI 的到来并非瞬间的宣告而是事后回顾的共识，警示其演进速度已远超人类建立安全机制的传统周期。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过历史纵向对比，指出 AGI 的到来并非瞬间的宣告而是事后回顾的共识，警示其演进速度已远超人类建立安全机制的传统周期。",
  "summary": "文章深度探讨了 AGI（通用人工智能）到来的隐匿性与紧迫性。作者通过回顾工业革命、核武器竞争及互联网发展等历史节点，提出「每次技术革命都在用上次的速度欺骗这次的人」的核心观点。文章指出，AI 的自主任务处理能力正以每七个月翻番的速度增长，门槛已在身后。与过去核威慑需要 20 年建立安全框架不同，AGI 留给人类调整的时间窗口极度压缩。此外，作者强调安全问题本质上是社会政治博弈而非纯技术问题，并认为在规则缺失的窗口期，既有的「信任」将成为放大新工具效能的关键杠杆。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AGI 的到来并非一个明确的宣告时刻，而是一个事后回顾的共识点。",
      "explanation": "历史上的重大革命如工业革命，身处其中的人往往难以察觉。AGI 同样如此，当社会意识到其存在时，它往往已经渗透并完成了对生产力框架的初步重构。"
    },
    {
      "point": "技术演进的速度正在呈指数级缩短，人类建立应对机制的时间窗口极度压缩。",
      "explanation": "从蒸汽机的七十年到互联网的二十年，再到如今 AI 工具以月为单位的迭代，人类历史上用于摸索边界、建立安全框架的「二十年缓冲期」在 AGI 时代已不复存在。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 安全问题的最终答案不在于技术参数，而在于复杂的社会政治博弈。",
      "explanation": "工程师无法独立定义安全边界，这涉及成本、公共利益和多方权力的平衡。正如伦敦大雾后的立法，AI 安全也需要经历现实的惨痛教训与社会共识的艰难达成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新工具的早期红利将优先流向在旧体系中拥有深厚信任基础的机构。",
      "explanation": "信任是难以通过工具快速产生的慢变量。在 AGI 规则尚未完善的窗口期，掌握传播渠道和信任资源的组织能最快将 AI 转化为杠杆，放大既有优势。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "每次技术革命，都在用上次的速度，欺骗这次的人。",
    "AGI 不会有一个到来的时刻，只有一个回头看的时刻。",
    "「多危险算太危险」，从来都不是工程师能回答的问题。",
    "人类用了二十年，才在核武器出现后摸清楚彼此的边界，而面对 AGI 的风险，我们这次没有二十年。",
    "最快拿到新工具的人，永远是在旧工具上建立了最深信任的人。"
  ],
